As a warrior, and seeing as I have never played one, I would think using two 1handed weapons with some spoofy procs would be better than a 2hander. Your entire purpose is as the main tank. Team up with a half smart SK some time, he/she can raise aggro sky high and let you single taunt it off then stand back for a moment while you gain more aggro points. <br>
